query:
SELECT dr.id, dr.branchId, DATE_FORMAT(dr.date, '%Y-%m-%d') as date, dr.total
FROM dailyRevenues dr 
WHERE dr.date >= '2026-01-01' AND dr.date <= '2026-01-07'
ORDER BY dr.branchId, dr.date;
